(2336)-Hertneck,G (2499) Vienna 2013 (0-1, 73)} Ncxd4 19. Nxd4 Nxd4 20. Rxc8 (
20. Bxd4 Bxd4 21. Bxh7+ Kxh7 22. Qxd4 Qf6 $15 23. Qd3+ Kg8 24. f4 g5) 20...
Qxc8 21. Bxh7+ Kxh7 22. Bxd4 Bxd4 23. Qxd4 e5 24. Qxe5 Bg4 25. h4 Bf3+ 26. Kh2
Be4 $36) (8. O-O Nf5 $17 {simply wins a pawn.}) (8. Na3 {is examined in the
next line.}) 8... Nf5 9. Na4 Qa5+ 10. Bd2 ({After} 10. Kf1 {Black can start
his counterplay immediately:} b5 11. Nc3 b4 12. Nb1 (12. Na4 Ncxd4 $17) (12.
Nb5 h5 13. Bf4 Bd7 14. a3 bxa3 15. Nxa3 Qb6 $15 16. Nb5 $2 {Pastor Alonso de
