Rb6 20. Rfc1 Rab8 21. Rc2 h6 22. g3 a5 23. Kg2 a4 $132 {Shirov,A (2713)
-Ivanchuk,V (2711) Monte Carlo (rapid, blindfolded) 2005 (0-1, 52)}) 12. Nxc3 (
12. bxc3 $2 b5 13. g4 (13. Nc5 Qxc3+ 14. Kf1 Ncxd4 15. Rc1 Qb2 $19) 13... Nfxd4
(13... Nfe7 14. Nc5 Qxc3+ 15. Kf1 $44 {Langhorst,T (1406)-Nordholt,U (1876)
