20. Qe3 Nxd3+ 21. Qxd3 d4 $36 22. cxd4 Qa5 $40 {[%csl Ga2][%cal Ge6f5]} 23. a3
$2 Rac8+ 24. Kb1 Bf5 $19) 17... fxe6 18. Bd3 Na4 $36 {[%csl Gb2,Gc3]}) 13. Nb3
{Not willing to give me a second chance to break the centre.} O-O-O 14. O-O-O (
{I planned to meet} 14. Na5 {[%cal Gd3a6] (threatening Ba6) with} Bg4 {[%csl
Ga6] , clearing the sixth rank for defensive purposes and the e-file for
active operations.}) 14... Bg4 {[%cal Gg4d1] I could not refrain from ensuring
