18. fxg3 Nxe5 19. dxe5 Qe7 20. Nd4 Kb8 $15 {[%csl Ge5,Gg3] x g3, e5}) 15. Rde1
h5 16. Nbd2 {Too passive.} ({White should have taken advantage of my move
order with} 16. Qe3 $5 {, since I was lacking the option ...g5-g4 followed by .
..Bh6. I planned} Bxf3 17. Qxf3 Qxf3 18. gxf3 Bf6 {, followed by ...h5-h4,
